Config.Description:
Default: ROOT_ACCESS_PASSWORD&lt;br&gt;
Once the database has been initialized this can not be used to change the password.&lt;br&gt;
Recommend removing value after the database has been initialized.&lt;br&gt;
Container Variable: MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD

OPTIONS:&lt;br&gt;
wiki = Backup mediawiki&lt;br&gt;
data = Backup database if you're using the internal MySQL add-on or SQLite&lt;br&gt;
assest = Backup file uploads&lt;br&gt;
all = Backup wiki, data, and assets&lt;br&gt;
false =  Do not do a backup during container start&lt;br&gt;
Container Variable: BACKUP_MEDIAWIKI
